159
00:16:31,754 --> 00:16:38,537
And that upon the written application, the board can make an extension for up to six months or for a period not to exceed six months.

160
00:16:38,557 --> 00:16:49,603
The way I'm reading that is that the six months is tied to the written application, but that there's no explicit prohibition on going back before the board to seek that additional six months.

161
00:16:53,016 --> 00:17:09,668
